---
title: Portobello & Orecchiette Primavera with Spring Veggies
description: Pasta alla Primavera is the ultimate celebration of Spring! Traditionally, people use whatever fresh Spring veggies they have on hand, thus, you'll almost never eat one that is exactly the same as the one before. Feel free to substitute with whatever veggies look good at your local market, but be sure to adjust cooking times, as not all veggies are equal!
